7 A Joint Resolution directing the Secretary of State
to refer to the people for their approval or
8 rejection a proposed amendment to Section 4 of
Article XIII of the Constitution of the State of
9 Oklahoma; stating certain parental and legal guardian
rights; limiting certain school regulations;
10 providing ballot title; and directing filing.
